{{Dialogue Start}}
:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504009001: Config/Level/Mission/5040090/Act/Act504009001.json-->
:What you see before you is simply an ordinary basket. As you can see, it bears no resemblance to a trashcan.
:However, among all the baskets... why does this particular one capture your attention?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} This... this must be fate...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} This basket has the soul of a trashcan!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Press "F" to assassinate.
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504009006-->
:'''Diogena:''' It's commendable that you recognize this is no ordinary basket.
:'''Diogena:''' However, this is my private domain, impolite one. Rain, wind, and sunshine are guests embraced, but not uninvited kings. You understand?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not really.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} But I'm part of nature, too.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Since when did Marmoreal Market become a personal property?
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504009011-->
:'''Diogena:''' ...Hmm, did I not make it clear enough? This basket is my home, and you keep your hands off and don't dig through it unless I say otherwise. Got it now?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
{{Dialogue End}}
